| 0 \< y ≤ 8     | <<<y[j] = j / 32, j = 1, ..., 256>>>    |                 |                      |                 |
*----------------+-----------------------------------------+-----------------+----------------------+-----------------+
| 0 \< x ≤ 8\    | <<<x[i] = i / 32, i = 1, ..., 256>>>\   | 0.50 ulps       | 3.64 ulps            | 694.0 ulps      |
