*----------------+-----------------------------------------+-----------------+----------------------+-----------------+
| 0 \< x ≤ 8\    | <<<x[i] = i / 32, i = 1, ..., 256>>>\   | 1.04 ulps       | 139.32 ulps          | 34509.0 ulps    |
| 16 \< y ≤ 256  | <<<y[j] = j, j = 17, ..., 256>>>        |                 |                      |                 |
*----------------+-----------------------------------------+-----------------+----------------------+-----------------+
